title: Number of births in Sweden 2009 to 2019
summary: In general Number of births has stayed the same over the Year.

Number of births is slightly increasing from 2009 to 2010, slightly decreasing from 2010 to 2011, roughly constant from 2011 to 2015, slightly increasing from 2015 to 2016, and finally slightly decreasing from 2016 to 2017.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
The highest Number of births, of value 117425.0 was reached at Year 2016
The lowest Number of births, of value 111770.0 was reported at Year 2011
